  ('@wttglobal', 'https://www.youtube.com/@wttglobal', NULL, 'UC9ckyA_A3MfXUa0ttxMoIZw', 'World Table Tennis', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'table tennis | ITTF | balls | Ping pong | World Tour | match | highlights | Table tennis Highlights | Table tennis Match Highlights | Table Tennis Compilation | International Table tennis Federation | Table tennis Serve | World Table tennis Championships | World Table Tennis | Ping Pong Highlights | Ping Pong Compilations | Ping Pong Match Highlights | Grand Smash | Nets | ITTF Highlights | wtt | wttglobal | 탁구 | 乒乓 | 桌球 | 卓球', NULL, 'Tennis da tavolo mondiale', 'Benvenuti nel mondo del tennis da tavolo!  World Table Tennis (WTT) è la società commerciale ed eventi della International Table Tennis Federation (ITTF).', 'World Table Tennis', 'Welcome to World Table Tennis!  World Table Tennis (WTT) is the commercial and events company of the International Table Tennis Federation (ITTF).'),
